Oauth2 server (client and resource server) based on nodeJS.
Base on following spec: http://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-oauth-v2-10

Tested with nodeJS v0.3.0.

Dependencies:
  - git submodule with --recusive option
  - libbsd-dev
  - xgettext and msgfmt (Debian package gettext)

To Install:
  make install
  make update_js_templates

To run the tests (need nodetk bins on the path):
  nodetests src/tests


To Generate the mustache templates (for web app):
  make update_js_templates

To update them (skiping i18n stuff):
  make skip

